VICTORY CONDITIONS

GAME ENDERS:
Incarceration,
Institutionalization, 
Homeless/Pariah/Outcast, 
Whistle-Blowing, 
Opposing Factions, 
stuck inside of a controlled institution. 


The Scion wins by achieving DEGRADATION OBJECTIVES and compelling the
NOBODY to 

	suicide
	life time institutionalized (prison, mental institution, hospital)
	reputation assasination

The Nobody wins by achieving ASCENSION OBJECTIVES and overpowering the 
Scion by

	Interceeding and saving lives
	Interceeding and saving minds
	Interceeding and saving souls
	Spreading Wisdom
	Raising Awareness
	Creating Beauty
